New Pine Creek first appeared as a [[census designated place]] in the [[2010 U.S. census]].<ref name=2010CensusCA/>

The [[2020 United States census]] reported that New Pine Creek had a population of 87. The population density was {{convert|38.4|PD/sqmi|PD/km2|sp=us|adj=off}}. The racial makeup of New Pine Creek was 76 (87%) [[White Americans|White]], 0 (0%) [[African Americans|African American]], 3 (3%) [[Native Americans in the United States|Native American]], 0 (0%) [[Asian Americans|Asian]], 0 (0%) [[Pacific Islander Americans|Pacific Islander]], 0 (0%) from [[Race (United States Census)|other races]], and 8 (9%) from two or more races. [[Hispanic and Latino Americans|Hispanic or Latino]] of any race were 2 persons (2%).<ref name=DP1>{{cite web |title=New Pine Creek CDP, California; DP1: Profile of General Population and Housing Characteristics - 2020 Census of Population and Housing |url=https://data.census.gov/table/DECENNIALDP2020.DP1?g=1600000US0651168 |website=US Census Bureau |access-date=May 30, 2025}}</ref>

The whole population lived in households. There were 46 households, out of which 5 (11%) had children under the age of 18 living in them, 18 (39%) were married-couple households, 0 (0%) were [[cohabitation|cohabiting]] couple households, 14 (30%) had a female householder with no partner present, and 14 (30%) had a male householder with no partner present. 14 households (30%) were one person, and 8 (17%) were one person aged 65 or older. The average household size was 1.89.<ref name=DP1/> There were 28 [[family (U.S. Census)|families]] (61% of all households).<ref>{{cite web |title=New Pine Creek CDP, California; P16: Household Type - 2020 Census of Population and Housing |url=https://data.census.gov/table/DECENNIALDHC2020.P16?g=1600000US0651168 |website=US Census Bureau |access-date=May 30, 2025}}</ref>

The age distribution was 11 people (13%) under the age of 18, 3 people (3%) aged 18 to 24, 7 people (8%) aged 25 to 44, 31 people (36%) aged 45 to 64, and 35 people (40%) who were 65{{nbsp}}years of age or older. The median age was 59.2{{nbsp}}years. There were 44 males and 43 females.<ref name=DP1/>

There were 65 housing units at an average density of {{convert|28.7|/mi2|/km2|disp=preunit|units&nbsp;|units|}}, of which 46 (71%) were occupied. Of these, 40 (87%) were owner-occupied, and 6 (13%) were occupied by renters.<ref name=DP1/>

